state: It's time to explore the amazing world of TextWorld! Here is how to play! First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to retrieve the cuboid keycard from the bowl. And then, move north. After that, make an effort to travel north. That done, head west. With that over with, check that the cuboid portal is unlocked with the cuboid keycard. Then, open the cuboid portal. And then, make an attempt to head west. If you can get around to doing that, make absolutely sure that the type 4 portal inside the study is unlocked. And then, open the type 4 portal inside the study. After that, attempt to move west. Then, assure that the gate is ajar. After that, go to the north. Then, go to the north. Next, pick up the keycard from the floor of the scullery. And once you've done that, you win! -= Cookhouse =- You've just walked into a cookhouse. You can see a bowl. The bowl is standard. On the bowl you see a cuboid keycard. There is an unguarded exit to the east. There is an unguarded exit to the north. > -= Cookhouse =-0/1
